text: Youssef Msakni (; born 28 October 1990) is a Tunisian professional footballer who plays as a winger or forward for Al Arabi on loan from Al-Duhail, and the Tunisia national team. == Honours == Tunisia * Africa Cup of Nations fourth place: 2019 == References == == Other websites == * * * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Association football forwards Category:Tunisian footballers Category:2022 FIFA World Cup players
